title: Studio 33 megamix series Collection
description:
Here's a collection of Studio 33 releases that I consider worth listening to. It means that most mixes produced after 2000 are not included. All mixes in the best quality I managed to find.

What's included:
Stories: 01-40, 44 (proper), 46 (ltd. edition), 51. Only 36th Story in 160 kbps, the rest in higher quality.
Party Compilation: 1-7
1/3 (artist megamixes): 1-3
Eurodance Party 1

Most mixes have covers and/or tracklists in text form.

If you happen to have 36th Story in better quality, please share.

And of course, enjoy!
